OL,7,FOn Tuesday, 2 December, two blue
OL,8,Fplaques - one in Welsh and one in
OL,9,FEnglish - were unveiled at the former
OL,10,FPriory Mount Hospital site, where
OL,11,FTerrence was born in 1945.
OL,13,FAt the unveiling the co-founder of the
OL,14,Ftrust, Martyn Butler OBE, described
OL,15,Fseeing Terrence's name on a blue
OL,16,Fplaque as "unbelievable".
OL,18,F"We are making so many advances in the
OL,19,Ffield of HIV it's a reminder sometimes
OL,20,Fof where we have come from, what it
OL,21,Fwas like 43 years ago," he said.
