OL,7,F"It was still a mystery illness, we
OL,8,Fwent through those terrible dark years
OL,9,Fof thousands of deaths, many, many
OL,10,Ffriends losing their lives, including
OL,11,FTerry.
OL,13,F"When you see it all encapsulated like
OL,14,Fthat, I am humbled and astonished by
OL,15,Fthe level of support that we have
OL,16,Freceived over the years."
