OL,7,FTerrence Lionel Seymour Higgins, known
OL,8,Fas Terry, was a figure whose life and
OL,9,Funtimely death would galvanise the
OL,10,Ffight against HIV and Aids in the UK.
OL,12,FHe lived in Haverfordwest for 18
OL,13,Fyears, before joining the Royal Navy,
OL,14,Fbut was later subject to a
OL,15,Fdishonourable discharge.
