OL,7,FDJ and Activist
OL,9,FFollowing his naval career, Terry
OL,10,Fbecame a DJ and music enthusiast. He
OL,11,Fregularly travelled to New York to buy
OL,12,Frecords, where he became involved in
OL,13,Fgay rights activism.
OL,15,FIn June 1982, whilst working as a DJ
OL,16,Fin Heaven nightclub in London, Terry
OL,17,Fcollapsed and was take to St Thomas'
OL,18,FHospital, where he was diagnosed with
OL,19,Fparasitic pneumonia.
