OL,7,FPneumonia was given as the cause of
OL,8,Fdeath. But Terry's family and friends
OL,9,Fwanted the true cause of death to be
OL,10,Fknown, so set up the Terrence Higgins
OL,11,FTrust - whose mission it is to end new
OL,12,Fcases of HIV in the UK by 2030.
OL,14,FLatest statistics
OL,16,FNew data by Public Health Wales
OL,17,Freleased this year showed new HIV
OL,18,Fdiagnosis fell to 73 cases in 2024,
OL,19,Fdown from 91 in 2023.
