OL,8,Fincrease in the number of tests
OL,9,Fcarried out, with more than 133,000
OL,10,Fpeople being tested for HIV.
OL,12,FPrescriptions for prevention
OL,13,Fmedication are at their highest number
OL,14,Fsince 2020.
